    paragraph4: "The success of the Street Team and the overall program hinges on trust, respect, and credibility. It is imperative to emphasize and uphold these values, which is why stakeholders, including law enforcement and criminal justice entities, understand and respect that information gathered by the Street Team remains confidential and is never shared with law enforcement or the criminal justice system. Clear boundaries are established and honored by all parties involved."
